Title: Tunnel Blockade
Text:
The goblins that Dwalthal Hammerbeard has asked you to clear can be found in the Water Works


Dwalthal Hammerbeard, the librarian of the Water Works expedition, has asked you to aid him by clearing the road leading to the 21st Hall of goblins.
CompleteText: Excellent! With that path clear again, it will be much easier to deliver supplies to the Twenty-first Hall.
